  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nErigon version: devel branch commit eb68c72d (also reproducible on release version and Ankr version)\r\n\r\nOS & Version: Linux Ubuntu 21.04 and Debian 11\r\n\r\nCommit hash : eb68c72d\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nTracing functions like `trace_block` and `debug_traceTransaction` should return the correct trace.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\nTracing returns error on almost all non-empty blocks\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n\r\nRun a BSC node without pruning.\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ curl http://127.0.0.1:8547/ -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" --data '{\"method\": \"trace_block\", \"params\" :[\"0x16b\"], \"id\": 0, \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\"}'\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":0,\"error\":{\"code\":-32000,\"message\":\"first run for txIndex 1 error: insufficient funds for gas * price + value: address 0x6488Aa4D1955Ee33403f8ccB1d4dE5Fb97C7ade2 have 0 want 110356250000000\"}}\r\n\r\n$ curl http://127.0.0.1:8547/ -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" --data '{\"method\": \"trace_block\", \"params\" :[\"0xc65d40\"], \"id\": 0, \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\"}'\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":0,\"error\":{\"code\":-32000,\"message\":\"first run for txIndex 670 error: insufficient funds for gas * price + value: address 0xa6f79B60359f141df90A0C745125B131cAAfFD12 have 15005000000000000 want 520238154086453897\"}}\r\n\r\n$ curl http://127.0.0.1:8547/ -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" --data '{\"method\": \"debug_traceTransaction\", \"params\" :[\"0x6971eb54baa66b420b6c58172bd1ff17e1119e2c11cfdc92c45eb920675c1bf6\"], \"id\": 0, \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\"}'\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":0,\"error\":{\"code\":-32000,\"message\":\"tracing failed: insufficient funds for gas * price + value: address 0x6488Aa4D1955Ee33403f8ccB1d4dE5Fb97C7ade2 have 0 want 110356250000000\"}}\r\n```\r\n",
